1c:T445,Internal evidence clearly describes a 4.5mm locking compression plate (LPS) with broad curved profile made of titanium alloy. External evidence from Meril's KET Trauma Fixation System catalog confirms this product belongs to the KET Locking Plate System family. Source_3 specifically references 'KET 3.5mm Meril Locking Plate System' with similar naming convention (LPS-Small Compression Plate), confirming the LPS designation. The product is a product_family representing a specific plate configuration within the broader KET system. Material specification Ti-6Al-7Nb is confirmed. However, brand field is empty when it should be 'KET' per external evidence. The 'ARMAR' prefix in product_family and brochure_heading conflicts with external Meril KET branding - this requires review to determine if ARMAR is an internal code, alternative brand name, or data entry error. Anatomy scope inferred from 'long bones' mention in description. Review recommended to resolve ARMAR vs KET branding discrepancy and confirm whether this represents a single product configuration or multiple SKU variants.17:["$","$L1b",null,{"product":{"product_name":"4.5 mm LPS Compression Plate Broad Curved","product_name_display":"4.5 mm LPS Compression Plate Broad Curved","sku_code":"MRL-LPS-016","product_family":"ARMAR 4.5 mm LPS Compression Plate Broad Curved","product_family_display":"ARMAR 4.5 mm LPS Compression Plate Broad Curved","slug":"4.5-mm-lps-compression-plate-broad-curved","images":[{"id":"prop_69c2d2d","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c2d2d07171238d2edca596/cover_637a9a77.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Pulsage Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":309736,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:17.906012+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"4.5 mm LPS Compression Plate Broad Curved | KET Locking Plate System Compression Plates - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_descr